[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0652","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0652.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0852","title":"IBM WebSphere 卸载脚本权限配置不当漏洞","description":"IBM WebSphere 在安装过程中对反安装脚本及其存放在 /usr/bin 目录下的数据文件设置了不当的文件系统权限，使得本地普通用户具备修改这些文件的权限。该漏洞影响在类 Unix 系统上部署的 IBM WebSphere 相关版本，攻击前提为攻击者已获得目标主机的本地登录权限。本地用户可利用该缺陷篡改反安装脚本或其数据内容，在后续执行反安装或特权操作时实施权限提升，从而以更高权限执行任意命令，危害系统安全。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0852"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:11.523","remediation":"升级到最新的WebSphere Application Server V9.0或更高版本，并确保应用最新的安全补丁包。升级前请备份所有配置和数据，然后按照官方指南执行安装过程，变更权限设置和脚本权限，关闭不必要服务，启用审计日志以监控权限变更。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/844","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8cc4bd87e08227d0a597e9249036a66efd1a35dd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0852.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0852","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0852.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a5bae259b1f96bb239cbfd83cd9b28dd6d9df406/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0852.json","https://github.com/zmerry/z-marvel.github.io/blob/581a79f0e7ceb8cdb3e444922154e004cca44bbb/vulbox/webvul/high/IBM%20Websphere%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-1999-0852).html","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0852.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/844/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--73507c5e-bd6a-43a5-ac88-f991430e8531.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0652.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0650","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0650.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0850","title":"Endymion MailMan 默认权限配置不当漏洞","description":"Endymion MailMan 邮件系统在处理用户邮件及相关文件时使用了不安全的默认权限配置，导致本地系统上的任意用户均可读取其他用户的电子邮件内容，或篡改、修改受影响的文件。该漏洞影响运行 Endymion MailMan 的系统，攻击者只需拥有目标主机的本地访问权限（如普通低权限账户）即可利用，无需远程网络访问或身份认证。利用方式较为简单，本地用户直接访问 MailMan 创建的邮件或数据文件即可越权读取或修改，可能造成敏感信息泄露及数据完整性破坏。建议管理员检查并收紧相关文件与目录的权限设置。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0850"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:11.300","remediation":"立即检查并收紧 Endymion MailMan 安装目录（如 /usr/local/mailman/）及其子目录（尤其存放邮件的 spool 目录和配置文件）的权限，确保仅 mailman 运行用户具有读写权限，移除其他本地用户的写权限。将 MailMan 以专用低权限系统账户（如 mailman）运行，而非 root 或共享账户。如不再使用该软件，建议彻底卸载并迁移至受支持的邮件系统（如 Postfix + Dovecot）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/845","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8cc4bd87e08227d0a597e9249036a66efd1a35dd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0850.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0850","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0850.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a5bae259b1f96bb239cbfd83cd9b28dd6d9df406/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0850.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wwpg-62fj-46fr/GHSA-wwpg-62fj-46fr.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0850.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1740993f-e6ae-45ce-80b0-f8b5f9578d18.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/76602871db1ff432e52b5609a116b2a5bc6fffe2/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0650.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0614","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0614.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0828","title":"SCO Unixware 7.1 pkg 命令缓冲区溢出导致本地用户可读取任意文件","description":"SCO UnixWare 7.1 的 pkginstall 及相关 pkg 命令（如 pkginfo、pkgcat、pkgparam）在实现存在缓冲区溢出缺陷。当本地用户以超长参数或特制输入调用这些命令时，可能触发缓冲区溢出，进而读取系统中的任意文件（通过 dacread 权限机制），造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响运行 UnixWare 7.1 的本地系统，攻击前提是攻击者需具备目标系统的本地登录权限，通过构造恶意输入调用相关 pkg 命令即可利用。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0828"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:08.580","remediation":"建议升级到 SCO UnixWare 7.1.1 或更高版本并应用 SCO 发布的安全补丁（如 osr507 安全补丁包）。无法升级时，可移除 pkginstall、pkgcat、pkginfo、pkgparam 的 setuid 位（chmod -s /usr/sbin/pkginstall /usr/sbin/pkgcat /usr/bin/pkginfo /usr/bin/pkgparam），或通过文件系统 ACL 限制普通用户对这些二进制文件的执行权限，防止本地用户利用 dacread 权限读取任意文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/853","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19660","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8d7a64f7f43d1af6189d4f7237515b997555b777/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0828.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0828","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0828.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c8b0fec8b23470355b47059dbab5d2ebdfa2ac94/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0828.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-234r-5236-88h3/GHSA-234r-5236-88h3.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0828.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/853/info.html","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000911.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0614.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0614.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0614.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0755","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0755.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0963","title":"FreeBSD mount_union 权限许可和访问控制漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统中的 mount_union 命令存在权限许可与访问控制缺陷，本地已认证用户可利用符号链接（symlink）攻击手段，通过构造指向特权路径的恶意符号链接，诱使 mount_union 以更高权限执行操作，从而非法提升自身权限至 root 级别。该漏洞影响存在 mount_union 组件的 FreeBSD 系统版本，攻击前提是攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限并能在目标文件系统上创建符号链接，利用方式相对简单，无需远程网络访问即可完成本地提权。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0963"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:25.107","remediation":"升级至 FreeBSD 3.3 或更高版本，该版本已修复 mount_union 对符号链接的检查逻辑。如无法升级，可移除 mount_union 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/mount_union）并限制可访问该命令的用户组，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6088","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/20b9340dcaffca733259fb153ac741206a5bbc5f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0963.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0963","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0963.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e90735e3e31fc62018265dfbae313d166e653462/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0963.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h2vr-vgcx-h595/GHSA-h2vr-vgcx-h595.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0963.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0755.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0658","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0658.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0859","title":"Sun SunOS arp 本地信息泄露漏洞","description":"这是实际的字段内容","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0859"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:12.377","remediation":"该漏洞源于 Solaris/SunOS 的 arp 命令在解析 -f 参数指定文件时，将解析失败的行直接以内存转储形式输出，导致本地用户可读到包含敏感信息的文件内容。修复建议：升级到已修复该问题的 Solaris 2.6 及更高版本（或应用 Sun 相应的厂商补丁），并限制 arp 命令的普通用户执行权限；在无法立即升级时，可通过移除 /etc/arp 相关脚本中可被普通用户调用的 -f 选项、收紧文件权限（如 chmod 750 /usr/sbin/arp）以及利用 sudo 规则限制 arp 的使用作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6994","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/837","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19232","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64fd197c5b8f3e4f9493cb07798bdca54583505c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0859.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0859","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0859.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9e7373a0dc9acbc4f26666870ca31dd641df9b83/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0859.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2x9f-j2ww-5cp9/GHSA-2x9f-j2ww-5cp9.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/837/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0859.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6b09661c-7e0c-40a8-8b6d-64fe7ae4f801.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0658.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0658.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0658.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0656","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0656.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0857","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9129,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10815}}","description":"FreeBSD 3.3 系统中的 gdc 程序存在符号链接（symlink）竞态漏洞。该程序在运行时以不安全的方式创建或写入临时文件，本地已登录的普通用户可通过预先创建指向敏感文件（如 /etc/passwd 或其他用户文件）的符号链接，使 gdc 在后续操作中误写入目标文件，从而篡改系统文件或越权修改其他用户的数据。该漏洞影响本地已获得 shell 访问权限的低权限用户，攻击条件为攻击者需能在目标系统上本地执行命令并控制当前工作目录下的文件创建行为，利用方式仅需在运行 gdc 前构造恶意符号链接即可完成文件篡改，无法直接实现远程攻击或权限提升，危害等级较低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0857"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:12.140","remediation":"升级到已修复该问题的 FreeBSD 3.3-STABLE 后续版本或 FreeBSD 3.4 及以上版本（通过 /usr/sbin/sysinstall 或 `freebsd-update` 更新系统并重新编译 base 系统）。如无法立即升级，可临时移除或限制 gdc 程序的 setuid 权限（`chmod u-s /usr/bin/gdc`），或限定普通用户对该程序所在目录及临时目录的写权限，以缓解本地符号链接攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/835","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19650","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64fd197c5b8f3e4f9493cb07798bdca54583505c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0857.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0857","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0857.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f71c1815da5fc1872d1d999eebe8b28a9e3854c7/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0857.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p372-4582-3p84/GHSA-p372-4582-3p84.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0857.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/eadba179b68570c488f1a812e4ac71e19ff05906/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0656.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0656.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0656.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0655","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0655.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0856","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9135,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10816}}","description":"Slackware 7.0 的 login 程序存在用户枚举漏洞，当尝试登录不存在或被锁定的账户时会返回不同的加密错误提示，远程攻击者可通过观察错误消息差异枚举系统中存在的有效用户账户。该漏洞影响 Slackware 7.0 系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，属中危信息泄露漏洞。攻击者只需远程访问 login 服务即可尝试枚举用户，无需认证即可获取有效用户列表，为后续暴力破解或社会工程学攻击提供便利。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0856"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:12.007","remediation":"建议将 Slackware Linux 升级至 7.1 或更高版本，并更新 login/util-linux 组件以修复该用户枚举缺陷。若无法升级，应修改 login 程序配置，使账户锁定、不存在及密码错误时返回统一的认证失败提示，避免因加密错误信息差异泄露有效用户名；同时结合防火墙限制远程登录来源、启用失败登录次数限制作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94416739411280&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2218edc43f34225d168835de417dff40749bef5/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0856.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0856","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0856.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2119b082f4927b0a9c902ed9fe95efb3b301cb81/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0856.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mphc-h5cf-cch2/GHSA-mphc-h5cf-cch2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0856.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000906.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0655.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0654","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0654.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0855","title":"FreeBSD gdc 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 3.3 系统自带的 gdc 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该程序在处理用户输入（如命令行参数或特定交互数据）时未对边界进行校验，导致攻击者可通过构造超长的恶意输入数据溢出缓冲区，进而覆盖返回地址并执行任意代码。该漏洞属于本地漏洞，影响范围为运行 FreeBSD 3.3 版本的系统的本地用户。攻击条件是攻击者需先获得目标系统的本地用户权限，随后运行经构造的 gdc 利用载荷即可提权至 root，从而完全控制受影响主机。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0855"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:11.897","remediation":"立即将 FreeBSD 系统升级至 3.3-STABLE 及以上版本（通过 /usr/sbin/upgrade 或源码 make world 重新编译安装 gdc 所在的基础系统组件）。在无法立即升级的过渡期内，可用 chmod 555 /usr/bin/gdc 取消其 setuid 位，并以 root 执行 chflags schg /usr/bin/gdc 防止被篡改，从而消除本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http:/