["epss"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:10.807","remediation":"建议升级到 Deerfield MDaemon 2.8.7 或更高版本，该版本修复了连接耗尽导致的拒绝服务问题。如暂时无法升级，可在 MDaemon 管理控制台中启用「IP 屏蔽」与「连接频率限制」，将单 IP 最大并发连接数调低，并通过防火墙对 SMTP/POP3 端口（25、110、143 等）设置每秒新建连接速率上限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94398020817351&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/68b3c685b96421db99cac9beb9d7bc8a6314be79/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0846.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0846","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0846.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/36499b7630ab4a32d11ab7c901b4c87271211bec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0846.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m57c-r3h3-p85x/GHSA-m57c-r3h3-p85x.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/M/mdaemon_dos.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0846.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--bba483a3-d379-47e8-8d7b-39d6ed224608.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/70290debf97c1057397e6f7c8c733dec0658bf76/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0645.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0623","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0623.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0838","title":"Cat Soft Serv-U FTP Server 2.5a SITE PASS 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cat Soft 公司出品的 Serv-U FTP Server 2.5 版本在处理客户端发送的 SITE 命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需与目标 FTP 服务建立连接，并发送特制超长的 SITE 命令参数（如 SITE PASS 后附加过量数据），即可触发服务进程缓冲区溢出，导致 FTP 服务崩溃并拒绝服务。该漏洞影响运行 Serv-U FTP Server 2.5 的服务器，攻击条件简单、无需合法账号，远程即可发起，但仅造成可用性破坏而非代码执行，危害程度中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0838"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:09.813","remediation":"建议升级到最新安全补丁版本（Serv-U FTP 15.x及更高版本），并严格限制FTP服务网络访问，仅开放必要端口。临时缓解措施包括更新服务补丁、配置防火墙禁用特定SITE命令，并限制远程用户权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/859","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19664","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a3a08d51f200d453300fca8b852aada6b8c5985a/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0838.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0838","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0838.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/44e56ab96b4cc04024678e20a1f15145c3b3cc59/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0838.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/1529.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/ftp_servu_path_disclosure.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0838.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/ftp.rules","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/859/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0623.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0602","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0602.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0826","title":"FreeBSD angband 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 3.3 系统自带的 angband 游戏程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该漏洞源于程序在处理用户输入时未对缓冲区边界进行充分校验，本地攻击者可通过向 angband 程序传入特制的超长数据触发溢出，进而执行任意代码并提升系统权限。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 3.3 版本，攻击者需具备本地登录权限才能利用此漏洞成功获取更高权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0826"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:08.333","remediation":"将 FreeBSD 系统升级至 3.4-RELEASE 或更高受支持版本，或通过 Ports Collection 升级 angband 游戏至 2.8.3 或更新版本以修复缓冲区溢出漏洞。如暂无法升级，可直接删除 angband 二进制文件（/usr/local/bin/angband）并移除相关端口作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1151","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/840","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19653","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/35cd604fbbf2927fb6acbcd700e81d36cd6dec11/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0826.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0826","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0826.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3a7f9488e77673498ec37285be0a165ad71720f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0826.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8934-gc3h-rh9x/GHSA-8934-gc3h-rh9x.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0826.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0602.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0593","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0593.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0823","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10806,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10827}}","description":"FreeBSD 3.3 系统中的 xmindpath 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该程序传递特制的 -f 参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 3.3 版本，攻击者需拥有本地账号才能利用，危害等级中等。目前官方已发布补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0823"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.957","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 到 3.3-STABLE 之后已修复该漏洞的版本（或升级至 3.4-RELEASE 及以上），并移除或限制 xmindpath 程序的 setuid 权限（执行 chmod u-s /usr/bin/xmindpath）。若暂无法升级，可通过 chmod 000 禁用该二进制文件，或使用 sudo 限制仅授权用户运行，避免本地低权限用户借助 -f 参数溢出提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1150","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/839","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19652","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/35cd604fbbf2927fb6acbcd700e81d36cd6dec11/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0823.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0823","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0823.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3a7f9488e77673498ec37285be0a165ad71720f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0823.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5rr9-3mvg-p33f/GHSA-5rr9-3mvg-p33f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0823.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0593.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0582","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0582.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0820","title":"FreeBSD seyon 权限提升漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统中的 Seyon 终端仿真程序（版本 2.14b 及之前）存在权限提升漏洞。该程序在运行时通过 PATH 环境变量查找并调用 xterm 与 seyon-emu 等外部命令，但未使用绝对路径，而是依赖相对搜索。本地已登录的普通用户可通过修改自身 PATH 变量，将恶意构造的同名可执行文件置于搜索路径前列，使 Seyon 在后续调用时执行该恶意程序，从而继承 Seyon 的运行权限并提升至更高权限（如 root）。该漏洞影响运行受影响版本 Seyon 的 FreeBSD 系统，攻击条件为本地用户访问权限及对 PATH 变量的可控修改能力，利用方式即构造恶意 xterm/seyon-emu 程序并劫持 PATH 完成提权。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0820"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.583","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 中的 seyon 至修复版本 2.14c 或随系统 ports 同步的最新版（pkg upgrade seyon 或重新编译 ports/comms/seyon）。如无法立即升级，应将 seyon 及其辅助程序 xterm、seyon-emu 安装到固定绝对路径，并以 root 运行 setuid 脚本时清理并设置受限 PATH（如 /bin:/usr/bin），同时移除 seyon 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s $(which seyon)）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/5996","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/838","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19609",