"score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0819"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.460","remediation":"升级 DeskPro 至官方已修复的 1.2 或更高版本；如无法立即升级，应在 Web 服务器（如 IIS/Apache）层面对 DeskPro 的查询接口部署输入校验与参数化过滤，限制数据库账户权限为只读，并在边界防火墙对 DeskPro 端口做访问控制以缓解 SQL 注入风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94398141118586&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/23264","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0819.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe9e77bf3808998cc7ef33bc8a5ea311f35fadb0/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0819.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0819","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c8b0fec8b23470355b47059dbab5d2ebdfa2ac94/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0819.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0819.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w2fr-8h6p-j4jg/GHSA-w2fr-8h6p-j4jg.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0819.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0581.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1006","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1006.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0853","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server 与 FastTrack Server HTTP 基础认证 缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 与 Netscape FastTrack Server 在处理 HTTP 基本认证（Basic Authentication）请求时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于服务端未对认证凭据的长度进行充分边界校验，远程攻击者可通过向目标 Web 服务器发送特制的超长 HTTP Basic Authentication 请求，触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存关键数据并以更高权限（如服务器进程权限）执行任意代码或命令。该漏洞影响上述两款 Netscape 服务器产品的相关版本，攻击无需身份认证，仅需网络可达目标服务端口即可发起，危害等级极高（CVSS 评分 10.0）。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0853"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-01","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级到已修复该问题的 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 SP2 及以上版本或 Netscape FastTrack Server 相应补丁版本；若无法升级，应在前端反向代理或防火墙处限制并过滤超长 HTTP Basic Authentication 请求头，或停止在互联网暴露受影响的 Netscape 服务器并迁移至受支持的现代 Web 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/847","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/68b3c685b96421db99cac9beb9d7bc8a6314be79/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0853.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2017/gb_netscape_fasttrack_server_auth_bof_vuln.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1006.toml"}]